<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
 <head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>CSS Display Property Showcase</title>
  <style>
   *{
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      font-family: "segoe UI", sans-serif;
    }  
    body{
      min-height: 100vh;
      background: linear-gradient(120deg,#020617,#0f172a,#020617);
      color: white;
      padding: 40px;
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }
    body::before{
      content:"";
      position: fixed;
      inset: -200px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle at 20% 30%, #00f5ff55, transparent 40%), 
                  radial-gradient(circle at 80% 70%, #ff00ff55, transparent 40%), 
                  radial-gradient(circle at 50% 50%, #00ff8855, transparent 40%);
      filter: blur(80px);
      animation: glowMove 12s infinite alternate ease-in-out;
      transform: translate(0,0);
      z-index:-1;
    }
    @keyframes glowMove{
    100%{transform: translateY(80px) translateX(40px);}
    }
  </style>
 </head>
 <body>
  <h1>CSS DISPLAY SUPERPOWERS ⚡ </h1> 
  <section class="block-demo">
  <h2>display: block</h2>
  <p class="desc">Stacks vertically. Takes full width. Create page sections.</p>
  <div class="box">Block 1</div>
  <div class="box">Block 2</div>
  <div class="box">Block 3</div>
  </section>
  <section class="inline-demo">
  <h2>display: inline</h2>
  <p class="desc">Behaves like text. Stays on the same line. Cannot set width/height.</p>
  <div class="box">Inline</div>
  <div class="box">Inline</div>
  <div class="box">Inline</div>
  <p style="margin-top:10px;">They flow like words in a sentence.</p>
  </section>
  <section class="inline-block-demo">
  <h2>display: inline block</h2>
  <p class="desc">Hybrid mode. Stayes in line but can have width and height.</p>
  <div class="box">Box</div>
  <div class="box">Box</div>
  <div class="box">Box</div>
  <div class="box">Box</div>
  </section>
  <section>
  <h2>display: flex(row layout)</h2>
  <p class="desc">1D layout engine. Align, center, space items easily</p>
  <div class="flex-demo">
  <div class="box">1</div>  
  <div class="box">2</div>  
  <div class="box">3</div>  
  <div class="box">4</div>  
  </div>
  </section>
  <section>
  <h2>display: flex(column layout)</h2>
  <p class="desc">Flex can also stack items vertically with perfect spacing.</p>
  <div class="flex-column">
  <div class="box">A</div>  
  <div class="box">B</div>  
  <div class="box">C</div>  
  </div>
  </section>
  <section>
  <h2>display: grid</h2> 
  <p class="desc">2D layout powerhouse. Rows + Columns at the same time.</p>
  <div class="grid-demo">
  <div class="box">1</div>  
  <div class="box">2</div>  
  <div class="box">3</div>  
  <div class="box">4</div>  
  <div class="box">5</div>  
  <div class="box">6</div>  
  <div class="box">7</div>  
  <div class="box">8</div>  
  </div>
  </section>
  <section>
  <h2>Creative Grid Layout</h2>
  <p class="desc">Grid can create magzine/ dashboard style layouts.</p>
  <div class="grid-art">
  <div class="box big">Big</div>
  <div class="box">Side</div>
  <div class="box">Side</div>

  </div>
  </section>
  <footer>Pure HTML and CSS no JavaScript.....yet...</footer>
   
 </body>
</html>
